---
---
<section class="output" id="output">
  <div class="output-inner">
    <div class="output-header">
      <h2 class="output-title">
        What you get back, <em>after the conversation.</em>
      </h2>
      <p class="output-sub">
        A full transcript. A focused summary. The moments that matter, already surfaced.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="output-composition">

      <div class="transcript-card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <div class="card-header-left">
            <div>
              <div class="card-eyebrow">Transcript</div>
              <div class="card-title">Senior Backend Engineer · Maya R.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card-meta">
            <span class="card-meta-tag">42 min</span>
            <span class="card-meta-tag">Voice + Video</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="transcript-body">
          <div class="transcript-line">
            <div class="transcript-time">02:14</div>
            <div class="transcript-content">
              <div class="transcript-speaker">Interviewer</div>
              <div class="transcript-text">Tell me about a system you've built or led that you're proud of — what made it work?</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="transcript-line candidate">
            <div class="transcript-time">02:21</div>
            <div class="transcript-content">
              <div class="transcript-speaker">Maya</div>
              <div class="transcript-text">So at my last company we had this notification system that was just constantly falling over. <mark>I rebuilt it around a queue with idempotency keys and circuit breakers</mark> — the thing I'm most proud of isn't the design, it's that we got from 60% reliability to four-nines without doubling the team.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="transcript-line">
            <div class="transcript-time">03:48</div>
            <div class="transcript-content">
              <div class="transcript-speaker">Interviewer</div>
              <div class="transcript-text">What was the hardest tradeoff you had to make on that project?</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="transcript-line candidate">
            <div class="transcript-time">03:54</div>
            <div class="transcript-content">
              <div class="transcript-speaker">Maya</div>
              <div class="transcript-text">Probably the decision to deprecate the synchronous fallback. <mark>It would have been safer to leave it in</mark>, but it was hiding the real reliability problems and giving on-call a false sense of security…</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="transcript-line">
            <div class="transcript-time">07:22</div>
            <div class="transcript-content">
              <div class="transcript-speaker">Interviewer</div>
              <div class="transcript-text">When do you reach for a queue versus a synchronous call?</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="transcript-line candidate">
            <div class="transcript-time">07:28</div>
            <div class="transcript-content">
              <div class="transcript-speaker">Maya</div>
              <div class="transcript-text">My default is synchronous unless I have a real reason. Queues add operational surface — DLQs, replays, ordering guarantees. I reach for them when…</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="right-col">

        <div class="scores-card">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div class="card-header-left">
              <div>
                <div class="card-eyebrow">Scores</div>
                <div class="card-title">Auto-evaluated</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="scores-body">
            <div class="score-dial">
              <svg class="dial-svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
                <circle class="dial-track" cx="50" cy="50" r="38"/>
                <circle class="dial-progress" cx="50" cy="50" r="38"
                  stroke-dasharray="238.76" stroke-dashoffset="31.04"
                  transform="rotate(-90 50 50)"/>
                <text x="50" y="50" class="dial-number" text-anchor="middle" dominant-baseline="central">87</text>
              </svg>
              <div class="score-label">Communication</div>
              <div class="score-sub">Skills</div>
            </div>
            <div class="score-divider"></div>
            <div class="score-dial">
              <svg class="dial-svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
                <circle class="dial-track" cx="50" cy="50" r="38"/>
                <circle class="dial-progress dial-progress--alt" cx="50" cy="50" r="38"
                  stroke-dasharray="238.76" stroke-dashoffset="19.10"
                  transform="rotate(-90 50 50)"/>
                <text x="50" y="50" class="dial-number" text-anchor="middle" dominant-baseline="central">92</text>
              </svg>
              <div class="score-label">Technical</div>
              <div class="score-sub">Skills</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="summary-card">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div class="card-header-left">
              <div>
                <div class="card-eyebrow">AI Summary</div>
                <div class="card-title">Auto-generated, reviewable</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="summary-body">
            <div class="summary-section">
              <h4>Bottom line</h4>
              <div class="summary-tldr">
                Strong technical operator. Clear on <em>reliability tradeoffs</em>, opinionated about defaults, owns the operational consequences of her design choices.
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="summary-section">
              <h4>Strengths</h4>
              <ul class="summary-points">
                <li><span class="marker">+</span><span>Explicit about tradeoffs, not just decisions</span></li>
                <li><span class="marker">+</span><span>Real operational ownership — measures herself on outcomes</span></li>
                <li><span class="marker">+</span><span>Healthy skepticism toward complexity</span></li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="summary-section">
              <h4>Worth probing</h4>
              <ul class="summary-points">
                <li><span class="marker">?</span><span>Cross-team disagreement examples were thinner</span></li>
                <li><span class="marker">?</span><span>Limited recent exposure to multi-region systems</span></li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="summary-footer">
            <span class="export-label">Export</span>
            <div class="export-formats">
              <a href="#" class="export-fmt">PDF</a>
              <a href="#" class="export-fmt">DOCX</a>
              <a href="#" class="export-fmt">ATS</a>
              <a href="#" class="export-fmt">JSON</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  section.output {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    background: var(--paper);
    padding: clamp(80px, 12vh, 140px) clamp(20px, 5vw, 56px);
  }

  .output-inner {
    max-width: 1240px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .output-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto clamp(48px, 7vh, 72px);
  }

  h2.output-title {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(32px, 4.6vw, 56px);
    line-height: 1.08;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  h2.output-title em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .output-sub {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(16px, 1.4vw, 19px);
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    margin-top: 18px;
  }

  .output-composition {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.3fr 1fr;
    gap: 24px;
    align-items: stretch;
    max-width: 1080px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .transcript-card,
  .scores-card,
  .summary-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .right-col {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .card-header {
    padding: 16px 22px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 12px;
    background: var(--paper-cool);
  }
  .card-header-left {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    min-width: 0;
  }
  .card-eyebrow {
    font-size: 10.5px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-mute);
  }
  .card-title {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--ink);
    white-space: nowrap;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
  }
  .card-meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 6px;
    flex: 0 0 auto;
  }
  .card-meta-tag {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--ink-mute);
    background: var(--paper);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    padding: 3px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .transcript-body {
    padding: 22px 22px 24px;
    max-height: 420px;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }
  .transcript-body::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
    height: 80px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, var(--white));
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .transcript-line {
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .transcript-time {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10.5px;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    width: 38px;
    margin-top: 4px;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
  .transcript-content {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
  }
  .transcript-speaker {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .transcript-line.candidate .transcript-speaker {
    color: var(--ink-mute);
  }
  .transcript-text {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
  }
  .transcript-text mark {
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent 50%, var(--accent-soft) 50%);
    padding: 0 1px;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  /* ── Scores card ── */
  .scores-body {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0;
    padding: 24px 20px;
  }

  .score-dial {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .dial-svg {
    width: 90px;
    height: 90px;
    display: block;
  }

  .dial-track {
    fill: none;
    stroke: var(--rule);
    stroke-width: 7;
  }

  .dial-progress {
    fill: none;
    stroke: var(--accent);
    stroke-width: 7;
    stroke-linecap: round;
  }
  .dial-progress--alt {
    stroke: var(--ink);
    opacity: 0.75;
  }

  .dial-number {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 500;
    fill: var(--ink);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .score-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink);
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .score-sub {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--ink-mute);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .score-divider {
    width: 1px;
    height: 80px;
    background: var(--rule);
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    margin: 0 4px;
  }

  /* ── Summary card ── */
  .summary-card {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    min-height: 0;
  }

  .summary-body {
    padding: 18px 22px;
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 14px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .summary-section h4 {
    font-size: 10.5px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-mute);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .summary-tldr {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--ink);
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }
  .summary-tldr em {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .summary-points {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 7px;
  }
  .summary-points li {
    font-size: 12.5px;
    line-height: 1.45;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    display: flex;
    gap: 9px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .summary-points .marker {
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    width: 14px;
    height: 14px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: var(--accent-soft);
    color: var(--accent);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-top: 1px;
  }

  .summary-footer {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    padding: 12px 22px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 8px;
    background: var(--paper-cool);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .export-label {
    font-size: 11.5px;
    color: var(--ink-mute);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .export-formats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 6px;
  }
  .export-fmt {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10.5px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    padding: 4px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: color 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .export-fmt:hover {
    color: var(--accent);
    border-color: var(--accent-soft);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .output-composition { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .right-col { flex-direction: row; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .scores-card, .summary-card { flex: 1 1 260px; }
  }
</style>
